Even though things were rustic, they didnt look dirty in the 2000s.

But post 2005, everything just got packed and rubbish was everywhere. Kathmandu today, is a farcry to what it was ~15years ago.

The whole vibe is so cool. Like a vintage album cover. 

The gymbros, 

the stonks bois, 

the  badass didibahini, 

pepsi factory workers wearing scientist labcoats, 

the mathletes, 

the punks, 

the film guys, 

the big bang theory computer nerds, 

the popular girls, 

the marching band.
